KMW Systems Corp said cofounderFred R. Klingensmith has resigned as a voting director andbecome an advisory or non-voting director.    The company said Klingensmith is founder and president andKRL Systems Inc, which plans to develop customized systemsbased in part on products bought from KMW.  It said he left theboard to avoid a conflict of interests but remains a major KMWshareholder. Reuter&#3;